{"tid":1385501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5號 基本上全公司得我一個唔返工都無意思！","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:21:34.000Z","uid":185981,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f00680c57c9c01779a02d57c5190b74649e3f915","tid":1385501,"uid":185981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UO0rx5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUO0rx5G.png&h=01710b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 作為一個成年人<br />\n眼見班學生班細路衝出去博埋條命幫你爭取，<br />\n你話你有屋企負擔 怕犯法 OK 我唔怪你。<br />\n而加只係叫你射一日波 罷工支持個運動都講埋呢d廢話。<br />\n有邊個無包袱 有邊個唔驚坐監 有邊撚個想個個星期行出黎日曬雨淋！！<br />\n你良心過唔過意得去！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果每個人都要見到成效 見到其他人做先跟大隊就唔撚係付出啦。你話你驚射完波返到公司比人秋後算賬。<br />\n咁你驚唔撚驚 ：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行出街都無啦啦人打，<br />\n著咩顏色衫都要考慮，<br />\n行過講一句唔岩聽既野就會比人告辱警，<br />\n黑警口頭定肢體上羞辱市民成為慣常，<br />\n司法制度淪陷，再無公義，<br />\n你既下一代連言論自由都無撚埋，<br />\n一國兩制無撚左 共產黨係剝削你所有人權同自由呀屌！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好諗咁撚多野，作為香港人，保衛家園，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日 全民罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBz4joq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBz4joq.png&h=43c31b73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a37d716966b94237d4b2181536f7ac97e0d71f6f","tid":1385501,"uid":185981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d5d6580724f08880f63b37d0780b0d39ad811cf","tid":1385501,"uid":186715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c03553bc5b65a24041163a531a0ce787d7018b52","tid":1385501,"uid":188132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7042a4a2e762592befd0860dcfe5cacc7c16338a","tid":1385501,"uid":185981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201